# HUMAN_ACTION.log (or .md mirror for repo)

Log of human-like actions performed by the bridge (mouse, keyboard, app control, vision).
Intended to be written by BRIDGE_HELPERS / app modules and read by task-engine for self-reflection.

Location when running: $env:USERPROFILE\GrokBridgeAssets\HUMAN_ACTION.log (or OneDrive equivalent).

This repo copy serves as template / seed + historical record.

